The paper deals with the problem of reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The focus is on sublinear algorithms, which are also relevant to the field of data structures (cs.DS). The paper also deals with optimization and control in uncertain environments, which are relevant to the field of systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper proposes a novel algorithm that involves variance reduction, which is a common technique in the field of mathematical optimization (cs.MA).
